  <div style="font-weight:normal; font-size:13px;">
  <h2 style="color:#666; font-size:22px; font-weight:normal; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd;">Vik Content Slider</h2>
  <p>Module to create Image or Content Slideshows.<br/><strong>How-to:</strong> Create a folder "vikcslider" in images/ and upload every image you wish to use in that folder. In case you want to make a slideshow of contents, create a file .html with the code or just text you want to view for each content to include in the slideshow. Put all these files into the same folder images/vikcslider/
  </p> 
  
